description: Ideally located and perfectly positioned, this grand family home and detached granny flat, is perfect for any large/extended family or any astute investor. This is a rare find, with a potential rental return of approximately $1,360 per week, this home is sure to attract a lot of attention from keen buyers. The moment you enter the main home, you will be greeted by an inviting foyer with double height ceilings and a flowing and practical floorplan. Quality tiling to ground floor, with an oversized formal lounge and formal dining area, study, extra large family/rumpus room with meals area. Large gorgeous gourmet kitchen, beautifully finished with granite bench tops, quality 900mm gas cooking appliances, dishwasher and water filtration. Spacious laundry, with downstairs powder room and internal access to the garage, with drive through access. Entertainers won’t be disappointed, with a huge wrap around alfresco area, complete with a fully equipped outdoor kitchen, including cooking appliances and large enough to host all your family and friends. Four extra large bedrooms await, with quality floorboards throughout. All bedrooms have built in wardrobes, with the grand master bedroom suite, complimented by the large walk in wardrobe and ensuite. Upstairs living area, offering additional living space and quality tiling and fixtures to all wet areas of this home. This wonderful home has recently been re painted throughout, with new flooring and lighting to upstairs and comes complete with quality external and internal light fittings, ducted air conditioning, alarm, CCTV cameras, remote controlled garage doors, three toilets and immaculately presented. The detached two bedroom granny flat is approximately 18 months old and is fully fenced with separate entrance. Masterfully built, with a modern and practical design in mind. Boasting an open plan, with quality tiled flooring throughout, LED lighting, two bedrooms, with built in wardrobes and a well equipped modern polyurethane kitchen, with stone bench tops, covered alfresco area and split system air conditioning. All this and more is set on a 620 sqm parcel of land. Being located so close to highly regarded amenities, including Edensor Park Primary School, Edensor Park Plaza, public transport, this home makes the ideal property purchase. Call today for more information.
